lmvvczerpmjMALLreSdBvy1XZ-YsTMRi0zENug9aj7aehV39zKsdR67Cc1sTnMvCTuiv9J_wFZU=
qZh]). People believed that the Sun rotated around the Earth, until Coperni=
cus showed them the light. As Rovelli wrote in The Order of Time:=C2=A0
That which seems intuitive to us now is the result of scientific and philos=
